respond with a hotspot in a
particular single location

00:10:27.660 --> 00:10:30.240
in this particular environment.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:32.640
OK, did you have a different
question about that?

00:10:32.640 --> 00:10:35.340
AUDIENCE: Yes, so
that all depends

00:10:35.340 --> 00:10:39.000
on the rat being conscious
of the fact that it's

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:39.610
in that place?

