00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:50.190
and he had no idea-- no
way to tell where he was,

00:10:50.190 --> 00:10:51.370
that wouldn't work.

00:10:51.370 --> 00:10:53.670
However, if the rat
knows the environment

00:10:53.670 --> 00:10:57.270
and then you do this in
a darkened room where

00:10:57.270 --> 00:11:00.240
he's actively locomoting
around, these things

00:11:00.240 --> 00:11:01.950
