00:11:12.520 --> 00:11:14.970
Remember I talked briefly
about the Tunisian ants

00:11:14.970 --> 00:11:16.890
doing dead reckoning.

00:11:16.890 --> 00:11:19.608
Keeping track of their vector
and speed at each moment

00:11:19.608 --> 00:11:21.900
and integrating the whole
thing to know where they are.

00:11:21.900 --> 00:11:23.108
That's called dead reckoning.

00:11:23.108 --> 00:11:24.495
Rats are pretty
good at that too.

00:11:24.495 --> 00:11:25.620
Another question over here?

00:11:25.620 --> 00:11:26.645
Yeah.

