00:21:51.890 --> 00:21:54.200
Usually in a rodent,
especially the same.

00:21:56.930 --> 00:21:59.390
Because rodents can turn
their heads a little bit,

00:21:59.390 --> 00:22:02.390
but mostly they're going
to keep it aimed the way

00:22:02.390 --> 00:22:04.100
they're moving.

00:22:04.100 --> 00:22:04.850
So I don't know.

00:22:04.850 --> 00:22:06.710
This is a long,
complicated excuse

00:22:06.710 --> 00:22:09.350
that I forget what
the answer to that is.

00:22:09.350 --> 00:22:11.150
But send me an email,
